#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"If the original message was deleted, the quote shows \"[mensagem "
"removida]\". Long messages are truncated in the reply preview. Editing the "
"original message updates the quote in all replies."
msgstr ""
"원래 메시지가 삭제 된 경우, 인용은 \"[mensagem removida]\". 긴 메시지는 응답 미리보기에서 truncated. 원본"
" 메시지 편집은 모든 답글에서 인용합니다."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_kick_notifications.html.heex:16
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
