#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_timers.html.heex:7
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Timer Types"
msgstr "타이머 유형"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_timers.html.heex:36
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"Timer commands run in the window that was active when the timer was created."
" If you switch tabs before a timer fires, the scheduled command still "
"targets the original window and your current window stays selected."
msgstr ""
"Timer 명령은 타이머가 생성되었을 때 활성화된 창에서 실행됩니다. 타이머 화재 전에 탭을 전환하면 예정된 명령은 원래 창과 현재 창이"
" 선택된 상태로 표시됩니다."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_aliases.html.heex:58
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Timers"
msgstr "계정 정보"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_timers.html.heex:2
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"Timers let you schedule commands to run after a delay or on a repeating "
"interval. Useful for periodic reminders, heartbeat messages, or delayed "
"actions."
msgstr ""
"Timers는 지연 또는 반복 간격 후에 실행할 명령을 계획합니다. 정기적인 알림, 심박상 메시지, 지연된 행동에 대한 유용한."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_contextual_tips.html.heex:7
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Tip Triggers"
msgstr "팁 트리거"

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_contextual_tips.html.heex:37
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"Tips queue if multiple triggers fire at once (2-second gap between toasts). "
"Tips do not appear while a dialog is open. Tips auto-dismiss after 8 "
"seconds."
msgstr ""
"여러 방아쇠가 한 번에 불을 던지는 경우 팁 (2-second gap between toasts). 대화 상자가 열릴 때 팁이 나타나지 "
"않습니다. 8 초 후에 자동 파견."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_display_settings.html.heex:7
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
